{"title":"问题1：节点间通路","date":"2020-06-27T07:39:32.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 27, 2020","L":"06/27/2020","MM-DD":"06-27"},"link":"2020/06/27/问题1：节点间通路","tags":["树与图"],"categories":["算法练习"],"updated":"2020-07-08T10:51:08.785Z","content":"<h2 id=\"题目描述\">题目描述<a title=\"#题目描述\" href=\"#题目描述\"></a></h2>\n<p><font size=4>  给定有向图，设计一个算法，找出两个节点之间是否存在一条路径（提示在页尾）</font></p>\n<h2 id=\"个人思路\">个人思路<a title=\"#个人思路\" href=\"#个人思路\"></a></h2>\n<p>  题目含义很明确，就是让手写DFS和BFS。而对于寻找路径来说，BFS是更好的选择。</p>\n<h2 id=\"个人解答\">个人解答<a title=\"#个人解答\" href=\"#个人解答\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">太久没写我居然写不出来BFS，很难受。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"题目解析\">题目解析<a title=\"#题目解析\" href=\"#题目解析\"></a></h2>\n<p>  -无解析</p>\n<h2 id=\"标准解答（bfs）\">标准解答（BFS）<a title=\"#标准解答（bfs）\" href=\"#标准解答（bfs）\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">static bool Search(Graph g, Vertex start, Vertex end)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            if(start &#x3D;&#x3D; end)return true;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            foreach(Vertex v in g.GetVertexs())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                v.state &#x3D; State.Unvisited;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Queue&lt;Vertex&gt; q &#x3D; new Queue&lt;Vertex&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            start.State &#x3D; State.Visiting;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            q.Enqueue(start);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            while(q.Count !&#x3D; 0)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                Node u &#x3D; q.Dequeue();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                if(u !&#x3D; null)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    foreach(Vertex v in u.GetAdjacent())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        if(v.state &#x3D;&#x3D; State.Unvisited)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            if(v &#x3D;&#x3D; end)return true;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            else&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                v.state &#x3D; State.Visiting;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                q.Enqueue(v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    u.state &#x3D; State.Visted;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            return false;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"复杂度分析\">复杂度分析<a title=\"#复杂度分析\" href=\"#复杂度分析\"></a></h2>\n<p>  如果是单链表实现的队列，其入队时间复杂度为O(n),出队为O(1)。这段代码的时间复杂度为O(n)。双链表则为O(1)。</p>\n<h2 id=\"反思\">反思<a title=\"#反思\" href=\"#反思\"></a></h2>\n<p>  基础知识不扎实，越是耳熟能详的算法越要自己亲手实现过才算是真正掌握了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"提示\">提示<a title=\"#提示\" href=\"#提示\"></a></h2>\n<p>  -有两个众所周知的算法可以做到这一点，其利弊是什么？</p>\n","prev":{"title":"面试经验汇总","link":"2020/06/27/面试经验汇总"},"next":{"title":"求职岗位调研（渲染相关）","link":"2020/06/26/求职岗位调研（渲染相关）"},"plink":"http://Ssssshinji.github.io/2020/06/27/问题1：节点间通路/","toc":[{"id":"题目描述","title":"题目描述","index":"1"},{"id":"个人思路","title":"个人思路","index":"2"},{"id":"个人解答","title":"个人解答","index":"3"},{"id":"题目解析","title":"题目解析","index":"4"},{"id":"标准解答（bfs）","title":"标准解答（BFS）","index":"5"},{"id":"复杂度分析","title":"复杂度分析","index":"6"},{"id":"反思","title":"反思","index":"7"},{"id":"提示","title":"提示","index":"8"}]}